@startuml
title Context Budget Flow
start
:AiRequest with history, retrieval context, memory;
:Estimate tokens with AiTokenEstimator;
if (Within provider limit?) then (yes)
  :Return request;
else (no)
  :Trim history and retrieval context;
endif
if (Fits after trimming?) then (yes)
  :Return bounded request;
else (no)
  :Reject with diagnostic category;
endif
stop
@enduml
